	* src/kahua/app/elua/html.scm :
	Modified form/cont to indicate input args' name as continuation.

	* test/greeting.kahua :
	Added for testing new form/cont

	* test/worker.scm :
	Added match&pick-form for testing form/cont, but i wonder if 
	it's correct. 

